'''東部省'''是[[斯里蘭卡|斯里蘭卡]]東海岸的一個省份。面積9,371平方公里。2001年人口為1,419,602人。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20,%20sex,%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |title=2001年人口普查 |access-date=2008-04-25 |archive-date=2012-05-17 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/67j70arpb?url=http://www.statistics.gov.lk/PopHouSat/PDF/Population/p9p2%20Population%20by%20district%20%2C%20sex%2C%20sex%20ratio%20and%20population%20density.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>首府[[亭可馬里|亭可馬里]]。下分3區。

1987年－2006年間曾與[[北部省_(斯里蘭卡)|北部省]]組成[[東北省_(斯里蘭卡)|東北省]]，後來被裁定分離。<ref>REDDY, B. M., [http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2321/stories/20061103003002700.htm Divisive decision] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2321/stories/20061103003002700.htm |date=20071013161744 }}. Frontline, Volume 23 - Issue 21 :: Oct. 21-Nov. 03, 2006.</ref>

